definitions.definition: A town in County Waterford , Ireland ( Irish grid ref X 0498 ) .
An island in Loch Linnhe , north of Oban , Argyll and Bute council area, Scotland ( OS grid ref NM84 ) .
A community in Pictou County , Nova Scotia , Canada .
A minor city and township in Nobles County , Minnesota , United States , named after the Irish town.
A city and local government area in the Northern Rivers region, New South Wales , Australia .
A town in the Shire of Corangamite , Victoria , Australia .
A rural locality near the Hinds River, south Canterbury , New Zealand .
